2025-12-03HCCanadian Centre on Substance Abuse ActAppointment of a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Centre on Substance AbuseAppointment of Susan Russell-Csanyi of Winnipeg, Manitoba, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Centre on Substance Abuse, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective December 10, 2025.N/A
